"Sip Solo...": **[Sue Ellen Francisco](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317162327/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Google-Web-Fonts&ffam=Sue%20Ellen%20Francisco%20-%20Regular&fid=8bc92811e2c416772332e731bb89054f&fsize=60&text=Sip%20Solo%20yo%20Sola%20Andando%20sola%20por%20ahi.&wrap=2)** by Kimberly Geswein [2010] part of Google Web Fonts

"Si el segundo...": **[Black Chancery](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317162327/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Dafont-1&ffam=BlackChancery%20-%20Regular&fid=753833d2833e9f73b56cffae357cf95f&fsize=60&text=Si%20el%20segundo%20de%20vida%20mas%20dulce&wrap=2)** free font (by From Doug Miles' Black Chancery bitmap font - Outlines by Earl Allen & Doug Miles. Public domain).

(...I have never encountered 2 fonts in a quest to find their names themselves!  
It could be a good fairytale to describe font forgery, plagiarism, orphan fonts etc.)
